 Background                                                         48 1451     
 -------                                                            48 1451     
                                                                    48 1451     
 This library was produced by the Low Energy Interaction Physics    48 1451     
 (LEIP) group at NC State University. The inelastic scattering      48 1451     
 thermal scattering law data for UO2 were developed using           48 1451     
 ab initio lattice dynamics methods [1,2]. The LEAPR module         48 1451     
 from the NJOY code system was used to produce File 7 MT=2 and 4    48 1451     
 for U in UO2 and O in UO2. Modifications to the LEAPR module were  48 1451     
 made to calculate the coherent elastic cross-section for UO2 [3].  48 1451     
 Per convention, MAT=48 and ZA=148 are used for U in UO2.           48 1451     
                                                                    48 1451     
