    Scattering Law for Uranium Dioxide," Transactions of the        48 1451     
    American Nuclear Society, v 115 (2016)                          48 1451     
 3. Y. Zhu, A.I. Hawari, "Implementation of a Generalized Coherent  48 1451     
    Elastic Scattering Formulation for Thermal Neutron Scattering   48 1451     
